dikishonale: Mtundu wa data ngati JSON wokhala ndi makiyi ndi ma awiriawiri
tulo: Mtundu wosankhidwa, wolondolera, wosasinthika wamtundu wa data
Zotuluka: Imasintha ntchito kukhala ntchito ya jenereta (yomwe ili yobwerezabwereza komanso yobwerezabwereza)
kupita: Mawu osunga malo omwe sachita kanthu
pitilizani: Idumphira ku kubwereza kotsatira kwa lupu
potsiriza: Yesetsani mutayesa / kupatula chipika mosasamala kanthu kuti cholakwika chinagwidwa kapena ayi
padziko lonse: Imalengeza zosinthika kukhala ndi mawonekedwe apadziko lonse lapansi
osakhala kwawo: Imalengeza kuti chosinthika ndi cha ntchito yakunja
yesani: Imayamba kuchuluka kwa ma code ndikuwongolera zolakwika
kunena: Imayang'ana mawu ndikukweza cholakwika ngati ndibodza
ndi: Amagwiritsidwa ntchito kwa oyang'anira zochitika kuti azisamalira zinthu
